comment._content: There's also a brief bio note on Louisa Macdonald in this 1894 Sydney Mail article...plus a sketch of the Women's College - news.google.com/newspapers?id=yTNVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=4pQDA... ; a pic of her appeared in the SM the following week, along with a sketch of the opening of the Women's College - news.google.com/newspapers?id=yjNVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=4pQDA... ; the T&CJ also ran a few articles on the Women's College at this time, including this one - nla.gov.au/nla.news-article71213774 There's also this 1892 Sydney Mail feature on Macdonald...plus a pic of University College Hall in the Illustrated supplement - news.google.com/newspapers?id=doAQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=wZUDA...
